data.description: Beautiful 1945 home with stunning upgrades. Home features ample natural light and hardwood flooring throughout. Living area and dining is located downstairs with bedrooms upstairs. Floor plan is easy for entertaining no matter the occasion. Large back yard with wooden back deck leading to a detached oversized garage that could serve multiple purposes from storage to workshop. Small town charm, yet 20 miles from Georgetown. This home is perfectly situated for country living with city conveniences.
